Tottenham Beats 9-Man Liverpool 4-0 in English Soccer’s Premier League

-- B y   J a m e s   C o n e
-- 
2011-09-18T14:26:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-18/tottenham-beats-9-man-liverpool-4-0-in-english-soccer-s-premier-league.html
Tottenham beat nine-man Liverpool
4-0 today in English soccer’s Premier League, with striker
Emmanuel Adebayor scoring two goals.  Luka Modric and  Jermain Defoe  also got goals at their
team’s White Hart Lane stadium.   Liverpool was trailing 1-0 when  Charlie Adam  received a
second yellow card after 27 minutes and allowed three more goals
after  Martin Skrtel  was sent off in the 63rd minute.  In today’s other games,  Manchester United  hosts Chelsea,
 Manchester City  is at Fulham, while Sunderland faces Stoke City.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Cone at 
 jcone@bloomberg.net  